QuestData.Title: Enemies Below
QuestData.Description: There are enemies of the Horde beneath this very city, $c.$B$BThe Searing Blade plots to take Orgrimmar for their own, and have already taken Ragefire Chasm! We need to storm their forces and retake what is ours!$B$BGo speak with Commander Bagran just inside Ragefire Chasm. He will have further orders for you.
